Apple may receive its standard app marketplace commission according to its policies, while the remainder goes to OpenAI.

Similarly, if you subscribe through Google Play, Google may receive the applicable store commission.

Current ownership (approximate)

Following OpenAI's restructuring, the ownership is approximately:

| Stakeholder                 | Approximate ownership |
| --------------------------- | --------------------: |
| Employees & other investors |                  ~47% |
| Microsoft                   |                  ~27% |
| OpenAI Foundation           |                  ~26% |


=====

This means Microsoft is the largest single shareholder, but it does not own or control ChatGPT by itself. Governance remains with the OpenAI Foundation.

